title: ROOTED ASUS Fonepad RAW ver 3.2.4 (dd 2013.07.26)
description:
ASUS Fonepad RAW,
Rooted by Botto00
(xda-developers)
d.d. 2012.07.26

This is the English version
Filesize: 803.652.710 bytes

To Install:

Copy this -.RAW to the Fonepad microSD card, in the root directory.
Disconnect any cables from the micro-USB connector.
Repoot the Fonepad by pressing BOTH power_on+Volume_Up (Hold).
When the logo shows "No USB connected", Press BOTH Volume_Down+Volume_Up.
Select the option "SD DOWNLOAD".

The RAW will load.
The APPs and Data will not be affected, if this is done correctly.
